<link href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=3394&amp;p=24649#p24649"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Allegro timer bug?]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=3394&amp;p=24649#p24649"><![CDATA[
<div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">      SECS_TO_TIMER&#40;secs&#41;  - give the number of seconds between<br />                             each tick<br />      MSEC_TO_TIMER&#40;msec&#41;  - give the number of milliseconds<br />                             between ticks<br />      BPS_TO_TIMER&#40;bps&#41;    - give the number of ticks each second<br />      BPM_TO_TIMER&#40;bpm&#41;    - give the number of ticks per minute</div><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=39">Zepper</a> — Sun Jun 03, 2007 9:11 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
